---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Maurice Calloway Jr."
  description="Concise snapshot: contact, experience, skills, education, and interests."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8 md:mb-10 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-600 to-emerald-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
          >About Maurice Calloway Jr.</span
        >
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 md:mt-8 text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Software Engineer focused on dependable platforms, clear goals, and thoughtful UX.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-10">
      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3 items-start">
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">Snapshot</h2>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li><span class="text-muted-foreground">Role:</span> Software Engineer (Level 60)</li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Org:</span> Microsoft — M365 Copilot Platform Infrastructure
            </li>
            <li><span class="text-muted-foreground">Location:</span> Seattle, WA</li>
            <li><span class="text-muted-foreground">Open to:</span> Frontend / Full‑stack roles</li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Email:</span>
              <a href="mailto:mlcalloway19@gmail.com" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                >mlcalloway19@gmail.com</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="text-muted-foreground">Phone:</span>
              <a href="tel:+12535614286" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                >(253) 561‑4286</a
              >
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">Summary</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed md:text-base md:leading-7">
            3+ years shipping platform and product features across management APIs, provisioning
            workflows, and developer tooling. Recognized for making systems easier to use and harder
            to break through actionable errors, modular architectures, and guardrails that reduce
            incidents.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-wide text-muted-foreground">Quick actions</h2>
          <div class="mt-5 md:mt-6">
            <div
              class="w-full flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-3 md:gap-x-5 md:gap-y-4 items-center"
              role="group"
              aria-label="Quick actions"
            >
              <a
                href="/documents/MauriceCalloway_SWE_L60.pdf"
                download
                class="inline-flex flex-none items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-5 md:px-6 h-10 md:h-11 text-primary-foreground shadow-sm hover:shadow hover:bg-primary/90 whitespace-nowrap transition duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                aria-label="Download resume PDF"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  stroke-width="2"
                  class="h-4 w-4"
                  ><path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    d="M4 16v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-2M12 3v12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l4-4"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                Download resume
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/maurice-calloway-ii-770568129/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex flex-none items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-input bg-transparent px-5 md:px-6 h-10 md:h-11 hover:bg-secondary shadow-sm hover:shadow whitespace-nowrap transition duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                aria-label="Open LinkedIn profile in a new tab"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="h-4 w-4"
                  ><path
                    d="M4.98 3.5C4.98 4.88 3.86 6 2.5 6S0 4.88 0 3.5 1.12 1 2.5 1s2.48 1.12 2.48 2.5zM.5 8h4V24h-4V8zm7.5 0h3.8v2.2h.1c.5-1 1.7-2.2 3.6-2.2 3.8 0 4.5 2.5 4.5 5.8V24h-4v-7.2c0-1.7 0-3.9-2.4-3.9-2.4 0-2.8 1.9-2.8 3.8V24h-4V8z"
                  ></path></svg
                >
                LinkedIn
                <span class="sr-only">(opens in a new tab)</span>
              </a>
              <a
                href="https://github.com/WestsideSage"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex flex-none items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-input bg-transparent px-5 md:px-6 h-10 md:h-11 hover:bg-secondary shadow-sm hover:shadow whitespace-nowrap transition duration-200 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-primary focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-background hover:-translate-y-0.5"
                aria-label="Open GitHub profile in a new tab"
              >
                <svg
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                  fill="currentColor"
                  class="h-4 w-4"
                  ><path
                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                    d="M12 .5a11.5 11.5 0 0 0-3.64 22.42c.58.1.79-.24.79-.54v-2.1c-3.23.7-3.92-1.56-3.92-1.56-.53-1.35-1.3-1.7-1.3-1.7-1.06-.73.08-.72.08-.72 1.17.08 1.78 1.2 1.78 1.2 1.04 1.78 2.74 1.26 3.4.97.1-.76.41-1.26.74-1.55-2.58-.29-5.3-1.29-5.3-5.75 0-1.27.45-2.31 1.2-3.13-.12-.3-.52-1.5.12-3.13 0 0 .98-.31 3.2 1.2a11.2 11.2 0 0 1 5.82 0c2.22-1.51 3.2-1.2 3.2-1.2.64 1.63.24 2.83.12 3.13.75.82 1.2 1.86 1.2 3.13 0 4.47-2.72 5.45-5.31 5.74.42.36.79 1.08.79 2.18v3.23c0 .3.21.65.8.54A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 12 .5Z"
                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg
                >
                GitHub
                <span class="sr-only">(opens in a new tab)</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Core skills</h2>
        <div class="mt-4 grid gap-6 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium">Technologies</h3>
            <div class="skills-row mt-3">
              <span class="skill-chip" title="C#">C#</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="PowerShell">PowerShell</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="KQL">KQL</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="React / TypeScript">React / TypeScript</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Swift">Swift</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="HTML / JavaScript">HTML / JavaScript</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="SQL">SQL</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium">Cloud / DevOps</h3>
            <div class="skills-row mt-3">
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Azure DevOps">Azure DevOps</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Azure Machine Learning Workspaces"
                >Azure ML Workspaces</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium">Tools & Practices</h3>
            <div class="skills-row mt-3">
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Mermaid">Mermaid</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Power BI">Power BI</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Wireframing">Wireframing</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="UI/UX">UI/UX</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Accessibility">Accessibility</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Dashboards">Dashboards</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Mentoring">Mentoring</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Post-mortems">Post‑mortems</span>
              <span class="skill-chip" title="Documentation curation">Doc curation</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Microsoft — M365 Copilot Platform Infrastructure</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
            Software Engineer (L59 → L60) • May 2022 – Jul 2025 • Redmond, WA
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
            <li>
              • Refactored management APIs to surface actionable errors, cutting debug cycles 50%
              and unblocking 8+ engineers.
            </li>
            <li>
              • Modularized provisioning workflows, doubling deployment speed and accelerating test
              iterations.
            </li>
            <li>
              • Extended DSVM lifespans in TDP sandboxes from 30 → 60 days, halving re‑provisioning
              effort.
            </li>
            <li>
              • Restored partner DSVM access in &lt; 24 hours, taking uptime from 0% → 100% (formal
              client commendation).
            </li>
            <li>
              • Safe‑deletion checks eliminated orphaned sandbox incidents (~5/mo → 0), ending
              data‑loss downtime.
            </li>
            <li>
              • Resolved Key Vault cert failures in COSMIC, restoring pipelines (0% → 100%) for ~10
              developers.
            </li>
            <li>
              • FHL 2023: 1st place “Best Security Project,” recognized by M365 VP Engineering.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
          <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">
              Microsoft — Software Engineering Intern (3 rotations)
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">May 2019 – Aug 2021 • Remote</p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
              <li>
                • Implemented a UI/UX proof‑of‑concept for the Euclid Workspaces team to improve
                scenario onboarding times.
              </li>
              <li>
                • Developed a management system enabling Tenant Admins to upload business locations
                in bulk within Microsoft Teams.
              </li>
              <li>
                • Used Azure Machine Learning Workspaces to analyze data‑usage patterns and identify
                partner teams.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">New Technologists Summer Academy</h2>
            <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
              New Technologist • May 2018 – Aug 2018 • Redmond, WA
            </p>
            <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm">
              <li>
                • Built Swift mobile app prototypes; partnered with engineers and PMs to strengthen
                product thinking.
              </li>
              <li>
                • Practiced rapid ideation, soft skills, and professional networking in a
                cross‑disciplinary cohort.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Education</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm">
            <span class="font-medium">Washington State University</span> — B.S., Computer Science (May
            2022), Pullman, WA
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground">
            Team Mentoring Program mentee; NSBE; WSU Wind Ensemble.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold">Interests</h2>
          <div class="skills-row mt-3">
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Weightlifting">Weightlifting</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Football">Football</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Basketball">Basketball</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Recreational Sports">Recreational Sports</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="League of Legends">League of Legends</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Euphonium">Euphonium</span>
            <span class="skill-chip" title="Trumpet">Trumpet</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Keep it subtle and theme‑aware; no custom colors here */
  .skills-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem; /* gap-2 */
    width: 100%;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .skill-chip {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    border-radius: 9999px; /* rounded-full */
    padding: 0.375rem 0.625rem; /* ~px-2.5 py-1.5 */
    font-size: 0.8125rem; /* ~text-[13px] */
    line-height: 1.2;
    border: 1px solid hsl(var(--border));
    background: color-mix(in hsl, hsl(var(--muted)) 60%, transparent);
    color: hsl(var(--foreground) / 0.85);
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    max-width: 100%;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .skill-chip {
      font-size: 0.875rem; /* text-sm on md+ */
    }
  }
</style>
